 imply that some QSEBs could be heated to Transition Region\ntemperatures, suggesting that IB profiles should be observed throughout the\nquiet-Sun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jul 2017 10:32:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-16"}
